text: Ilian Iliev (born 2 August 1966) is a Bulgarian equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Bulgaria Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
